data.title: Catholic Church of St. Ann, Marietta, GA. La Salette Parish
data.text:
The St. Ann columbarium is a sacred resting place on holy ground for cremated human remains with the same dignity as a cemetery. Dedicated by Archbishop Wilton D. Gregory in 2017, it is a place for our loved ones to rest until our Lord comes again; a place at home in our beloved community and church. Our columbarium offers a very peaceful place for you to come and pray.

At this time, there are no columbarium niches available for purchase. For more information, please contact Linda Walsh.
